  & {{Mago}} laughed, relaxing for the first time in a week. A large crowd encircled them at the town hall then, the suns were about to set, it was time. Everyone around fell quiet, and watched as the doors leading inside the town hall swung open. Lupin gulped, even a funny-looking scarf wouldn't be enough to calm {{Mago}}'s nerves now, but even so, this youngling always knew what to say in such times…

  & "Let's go inside–OH Venerable Nose Hair of the Ilk!"

